gameRecap.title: Game Recap: Magic 113, Bulls 98
gameRecap.excerpt: The Magic defeated the Bulls, 113-98. Paolo Banchero led the way for the Magic with 24 points, six rebounds and five assists, while Jalen Suggs added 19 points (3-6 3PT FG) and five assists in the victory. DeMar DeRozan led all scorers with 30 points and five assists for the Bulls in the losing effort. The Magic improve to 46-32 on the season, while the Bulls fall to 37-41.
